parse_smiles

parse_smiles.Rd

simple smiles parser

parse_smiles(smi, generatecoords = TRUE, kekulise = TRUE)

Arguments

smi

Required. A smiles string
generatecoords

Optional. Default TRUE. Whether to generate coordinates from the smiles
kekulise

Optional. Boolean. Default TRUE

Examples
